==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Yellowlegs
<hw>Yel"low*legs`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>Any one of several species of long-legged sandpipers of the genus
<gen>Totanus</gen>, in which the legs are bright yellow; -- called also
<altname>stone snipe</altname>, <altname>tattler</altname>,
<altname>telltale</altname>, <altname>yellowshanks</altname>; and
<altname>yellowshins</altname>. See <er>Tattler</er>, 2.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Yellowness</ent>⟦br⟧
